[![Top Language](https://img.shields.io/github/languages/top/Salah-Diouane/ft_transcendence?style=for-the-badge)](https://github.com/Salah-Diouane/ft_transcendence)

A real-time multiplayer web application built as the final 42 project.
Featuring online gameplay, chat, and advanced authentication — powered by Socket.IO, JWT, and modern web frameworks.

## 🚀 Overview

**ft_transcendence** is a full-stack web platform that allows authenticated users to play games, chat, and compete with others online — all in real time.

It demonstrates mastery of modern web technologies, robust authentication systems (JWT + 2FA + OAuth), and a scalable architecture using WebSockets.

