## 🧩 Features

* **⚙️ Modern Backend Framework:** Built with **NestJS** (or Express.js), providing:
    * A robust RESTful API for all core actions.
    * WebSocket-based real-time events via **Socket.IO**.
    * A modular and scalable server architecture.

* **👥 Secure User Management:**
    * Secure user registration and login.
    * **JWT-based** session management for persistent authentication.

* **🌍 Remote Authentication (OAuth2):**
    * Integration with a remote OAuth2 provider (e.g., **42 API**, Google).
    * Allows external identity verification and seamless login.

* **🎮 Real-time Multiplayer:**
    * Live matchmaking and gameplay synchronization using **Socket.IO**.
    * A smooth, low-latency experience for remote users.

* **🕹️ Multiple Games & History:**
    * Includes the classic game **Pong** plus at least one other game.
    * Persistent game history tracking and user statistics.

* **💬 Live Chat:**
    * Real-time global and private chat channels.
    * Integrated chat functionality within game rooms and lobbies.

* **🔐 Advanced Security:**
    * Optional **Two-Factor Authentication (2FA)** for stronger account security.
    * Stateless session authentication using JWT tokens.

* **⚛️ Modern Frontend:**
    * Developed using **React** or **Next.js**.
    * Real-time UI updates driven by Socket.IO events.
    * A clean and modern UX styled with **TailwindCSS**.

* **🗄️ Database Integration:**
    * Persistent data storage using **PostgreSQL**.
    * Data managed efficiently with **Prisma ORM** (or TypeORM).

* **📱 Responsive & Accessible:**
    * Fully responsive design for desktop, tablet, and mobile.
    * Multi-language support (e.g., English, French, Arabic).
    * Cross-browser compatibility (Chrome, Firefox, Edge, Safari).

## 🏗️ Tech Stack

| Layer | Technology |
| :--- | :--- |
| **Frontend** | Next.js / React, TailwindCSS, Socket.IO Client |
| **Backend** | NestJS / Express.js, Socket.IO, JWT, OAuth2 |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL + Prisma ORM |
| **Auth** | JWT, 2FA, OAuth (42 API / Google) |
| **Deployment** | Docker, Nginx, HTTPS |
| **Monitoring** | Prometheus, Grafana (optional) |

